<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2347">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qing-ling-zhi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qing-ling-zhi" class="zg-link" title="卿伶直">卿伶直</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiaoqing-gong" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiaoqing-gong" class="zg-link" title="xiaoqing Gong">xiaoqing Gong</a></span>
